This directory contains binary versions of the RML system.
Please read the file INSTALL for installation instructions.

Please read the file NEWS for a summary of user-visible changes
made in each intermediate release.

The elisp directory contains a simple RML mode for Gnu Emacs.
Also a mode for rml debug.

The examples hierarchy contains some working applications constructed
using RML.

The doc contains DEBUG.txt on how to use/run the debugger

COPYRIGHT contains the RML copyright notice, license and disclaimer.

More information about RML can be found in
http://www.ida.liu.se/~pelab/rml


This package was created
and is maintained by:
